It has the same hole mounting pattern as the Norton 8500 series, allowing it to replace old and worn out closers without having to drill new holes or having to replace the door or frame.

title: Cal Royal CRCODE007LH Electronic Keyless Door Locks Left Handed
description: The Cal Royal Electronic Keyless Door Locks Left Handed CRCODE007LH is an electronic heavy duty keyless lock. Instead of using a key to gain access through the door, you can set a code on a pushbutton panel to unlock the door. This version of the keyless door lock can store up to 90 different numeric codes of 4, 5, or 6 digits.

title: Cal Royal ESC2200 ALUM Lever Panic Bar Trim
description: ESC2200 panic bar trim is a lever with a cylinder controlling the locking mode of the lever. The lever is rigid: it is not always able to move. When in the unlocked mode the lever is engaged with the panic bar and activates the latch to allow access. When the lever is in the lock mode, the lever does not move and does not activate the panic bar or allow access.
